*Community Pool &amp; Clubhouse<br>
*Basic Cable &amp; Internet, Trash and Lawn Included!!<br>
*One Assigned Parking Spot- Visitor Parking Available<br>
*Perfect location – off St. Rd. 54 between Little Rd. &amp; Seven Springs. Close to shopping &amp; restaurants.<br>
*2 pet limit and small pets only!! (No taller than 16 inches in height per HOA)<br>
